2000001.name: How will you fare against my blade?

2000003.name: One day I'll surpass my father!

2000004.name: I want to fight stronger opponents!

2000011.name: Lava was defeated? You expect me to believe that?

2000012.name: Get out of my way! My fight is with Lava!

2000013.name: Darn! I guess I didn't have what it takes!

2000022.name: You're not bad. You've piqued my interest.

2000023.name: To face a strong opponent is every warrior's dream.

2000024.name: How interesting! Show me more of what you've got!

2000031.name: I've no time to play around with you.

2000032.name: You might be difficult to deal with.

2000034.name: Looks like you're more than just talk.

2000041.name: It seems you aren't just a simple soldier.

2000043.name: Grafl! Pay attention! This one's quite capable!

2000051.name: Who's this? You're a strange one, aren't ya?

2000054.name: Let us show you our joint attack!

2000061.name: How odd...my blade is reacting to you.

2000062.name: How could such a warrior exist?

2000063.name: Allow me to show you my special move! Aurora!!

2000064.name: Allow me to see the burning fire in your heart!

2000065.name: My blade is like the fire of hades!

2000075.name: Even gods don't have the right to destroy people!

2000076.name: No giving up! I've still got some fight in me!

2000082.name: Have some Phoenix breast for all your hard work!

2000083.name: Let me cook something up for you!

2000084.name: Hold on! It's not ready yet!

2000085.name: The main dish is almost ready!

2000092.name: What is a god? Who is truly evil!?

2000093.name: I'm the thief who's going to steal your lives!

2000101.name: Let me fix your weapons for you!

2000102.name: Darn it! There's just no end to it!

2000103.name: Hey, hero! Are you using my weapons properly?

2000111.name: I'll burn everything, even the gods!

2000112.name: I can hear them. Wings! Come to your hero!

2000114.name: Let me show you the power of the black flame!

2000115.name: I'm defeated... Looks like I won't be seeing him now...

2000122.name: My life belongs to the empire!

2000124.name: My army will not be defeated so easily! Forward march!

2000132.name: To the one who noticed me...

2000133.name: I will take you with me!

2000134.name: I like it here! Away with you!

2000143.name: Check out these wings! I feel invincible!

2000148.name: This is the power of his wings!

2000149.name: Bring it on! I've still got a lot left!

2000181.name: I won't leave until I've accomplished my objective.

2000182.name: I'll show you Drevas' true power.

2000185.name: I guess I haven't matured enough.

2000191.name: I haven't seen you around here before.

2000192.name: I won't forgive you for what you did to Falma!

2000193.name: You dare defy those you have no chance of beating?

2000194.name: Falma! Time to show our true power!

2000202.name: I won't be done in by a youngster!

2000212.name: I won't make the same mistake again!

2000221.name: Youngster, what is it that you fight for?

2000222.name: The path to your dreams is full of hardship.

2000223.name: Can you go on, knowing the Demon Pike's curse?

2000224.name: Focus your will and free the World Tree.

2000241.name: I won't forgive any who cause harm to this forest.

2000242.name: A massive power is asleep just ahead.

2000244.name: Do not involve us in your quarrel!

2000261.name: Do you know the true identity of the Demon Pike?

2000262.name: When the World Tree awakens so will the forest.

2000263.name: I must protect the peace of the forest!

2000264.name: The person inside of me is excited.

2000265.name: It is impossible to deny the passage of time.

2000266.name: I recognize you as one cursed by the Demon Pike.

2000272.name: Still not enough... I need more...

2000273.name: Allow me to absorb your energy!

2000282.name: Who are you who disturbs my slumber?

2000283.name: Be not reckless, ye who is cursed by the Demon Pike.

2000284.name: My family, allow me to heal your wounds.
